---
title: Seared Sumac Chicken with Tangy Carrot & Cucumber Ribbon Salad and Toasted Pitas
description: Chicken thighs are seared and cooked perfectly after being coated with garlic, sumac and oil! Severed with a sweet and tangy veggie ribbon salad and a warm toasted pita, tonights 30-minute dinner is perfect for any spring night!
